title: 701: BITCOIN ‘HEAVY BREAKOUT’ FRACTAL SUGGEST BTC PRICE WILL HIT $250K-$350K IN 2021!!!!
description:
Bitcoin has the potential to push its prices to between $250K-$350K by the end of 2021, a long-standing fractal suggests.

The analogy appeared in anticipation that Bitcoin could post a 2017-like bull run, in which the price rose by more than 1,900%.

"Somewhere 2017 we are. Heavy breakout to come at a later stage to ~$250-350K and then landing on $65K in the bear market for Bitcoin."
